  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, combine yeast and warm water. Let it sit for 5 minutes until foamy.",
    "Add sugar and melted butter. Mix well.",
    "Add the egg substitute and mix until the mixture is smooth.",
    "Add the flour, chickpeas, oregano, rosemary, and salt. Mix until a dough forms.",
    "Knead the dough for 10 minutes until it becomes smooth and elastic.",
    "Place the dough in a greased bowl, cover it with plastic wrap, and let it rise in a warm place for 1 hour.",
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Punch down the dough and shape it into a round loaf.",
    "Place the loaf on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Brush the top of the loaf with melted butter.",
    "Bake for 35-40 minutes until the bread is golden brown.",
    "Remove from the oven and let it cool for 10 minutes before slicing."
  ],
